More parody cards + tune arena so it's a supplement, not main income

- CardCatalog: +12 parody-pun cards (Ederzone, Keylor Naptime, Ruben
  Diabolical, Toni Crouton, Kant-Stop, Vlahovroom, Victor Osi-When?, etc.)
  across GK/DEF/MID/FWD and Rare→Legendary. Transformative puns only.
- HubService arena balance: coin orbs 300-1200 -> 120-420, spawn 1-2 (was
  1-3) up to 6 (was 8); KOTH trickle 70/s -> 50/s. The arena is now a fun
  bonus rather than out-earning your stadium.

